msgstr "Permutations part 2"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="178"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.143"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.5.4.12"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1397"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.12.1"
msgid "Paṭiggaṇhāti vīmaṃsati paccāharati, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"If he accepts the mission, finds out the response, and reports back, he "
"commits an offense entailing suspension."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.12.2"
msgid "Paṭiggaṇhāti vīmaṃsati na paccāharati, āpatti thullaccayassa."
msgstr ""
"If he accepts the mission, and finds out the response, but does not report "
"back, he commits a serious offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.12.3"
msgid "Paṭiggaṇhāti na vīmaṃsati paccāharati, āpatti thullaccayassa."
msgstr ""
"If he accepts the mission, but does not find out the response, yet reports "
"back, he commits a serious offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.12.4"
msgid "Paṭiggaṇhāti na vīmaṃsati na paccāharati, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If he accepts the mission, but neither finds out the response, nor reports "
"back, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.12.5"
msgid "Na paṭiggaṇhāti vīmaṃsati paccāharati, āpatti thullaccayassa."
msgstr ""
"If he does not accept the mission, yet finds out the response and reports "
"back, he commits a serious offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.12.6"
msgid "Na paṭiggaṇhāti vīmaṃsati na paccāharati, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If he does not accept the mission, yet finds out the response, but does not "
"report back, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.12.7"
msgid "Na paṭiggaṇhāti na vīmaṃsati paccāharati, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If he neither accepts the mission, nor finds out the response, yet reports "
"back, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.12.8"
msgid "Na paṭiggaṇhāti na vīmaṃsati na paccāharati, anāpatti."
msgstr ""
"If he does not accept the mission, nor finds out the response, nor reports "
"back, there is no offense."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="179"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.5.4.13"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1398"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.13.1"
msgid "Puriso sambahule bhikkhū āṇāpeti—"
msgstr "A man tells a number of monks,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.13.2"
msgid "“gacchatha, bhante, itthannāmaṃ itthiṃ vīmaṃsathā”ti."
msgstr "“Venerables, find out about such-and-such a woman.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.13.3"
msgid ""
"Sabbe paṭiggaṇhanti sabbe vīmaṃsanti sabbe paccāharanti, āpatti sabbesaṃ "
"saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"If they all accept the mission, all find out the response, and all report "
"back, they all commit an offense entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="180"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1399"></a> 
