msgid ""
"Sabbe paṭiggaṇhanti ekaṃ vīmaṃsāpetvā sabbe paccāharanti, āpatti sabbesaṃ "
"saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"If they all accept the mission, but only one finds out the response, yet all "
