"report back, he commits an offense entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="185"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1404"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.14.7"
msgid "Puriso bhikkhuṃ āṇāpeti—"
msgstr "A man tells a monk,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.14.8"
msgid "“gaccha, bhante, itthannāmaṃ itthiṃ vīmaṃsā”ti."
msgstr "“Venerable, find out about such-and-such a woman.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.14.9"
msgid ""
"Paṭiggaṇhāti antevāsiṃ vīmaṃsāpetvā attanā paccāharati, āpatti "
"saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"If he accepts the mission, but gets a pupil to find out the response, and "
"then reports back himself, he commits an offense entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="186"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1405"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss5:pts-cs4.14.10"
